BT 1 0 0 1 0 111 Tm 12 TL /F1 9 Tf 0 0 0 rg (Death has not been formally defined within the Wike framework. This paper does so. Death is the irreversible termination of) Tj T* (the Bootstrap loop -- the point at which the biological Szilard engine \(Paper 45\) can no longer pay its own Landauer cost,) Tj T* (gamma_eff diverges without bound, and the coherent state C -) Tj (> 0. This is a phase transition, not annihilation. The First Law) Tj T* (of Thermodynamics prohibits the destruction of the energy that constituted the coherent state. Landauer's Principle \(Paper) Tj T* (45\) establishes that the information encoded in that state cannot vanish without equivalent heat dissipation. What the) Tj T* (framework can map: the approach to death, the transition point, and the immediate post-transition thermodynamic) Tj T* (consequences. What the framework cannot map: what the energy-information state becomes beyond the biological) Tj T* (boundary. That is a genuine singularity -- the equations break at the same point, for the same reason, as all known physics) Tj T* (singularities. The paper closes with the clinical implications that are fully within the framework's reach: how to identify when) Tj T* (the window \(Paper 44\) is closing, and what interventions the physics supports.) Tj T* ET
